@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<section class="hero">
    <div class="glass">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="lead">How MoWow 3.3.5 collects, stores, and protects your data.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="stats-section">
    <div class="glass">

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif)">1. What We Store</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>The email address you register with.</li>
            <li>A salted &amp; hashed copy of your password (never plain text).</li>
            <li>Your in-game account name and character data (held by AzerothCore).</li>
            <li>IP address and timestamp for security logs.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif)">2. What We Never Store</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>No payment or billing information (the server is free).</li>
            <li>No third-party analytics cookies.</li>
            <li>No personal metadata beyond the bullets above.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif)">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p>
            Solely to authenticate you on the website and in-game realm,
            prevent abuse, and maintain leaderboards / characters.
            We do <em>not</em> sell or share your information with anyone.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif)">4. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
            The site sets one secure cookie: <code>.MoWowAuth</code>.
            It contains only an encrypted session identifier to keep you logged in.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif)">5. Data Removal</h2>
        <p>
            Email <a href="mailto:ravaeimohamad@gmail.com">ravaeimohamad@gmail.com</a> from the
            address you registered with and request deletion.
            Your website account and game characters will be wiped within 72 hours.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif)">6. Contact</h2>
        <p>
            For any privacy questions reach out via email or DM on
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mohamad_ravaei/" target="_blank">Instagram</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
